Rating: 4
After reading reviews, I was skeptical but my husband heard roasted garlic and said go fo it. This was one of three entrees planned for a buffet on NYE for 18. It was wonderful and everyone loved it. The sauce was delicate enough to not overpower the scallops. I did make a few changes.....I added an extra head of roasted garlic and more lemon juice. As to the greens, I wilted the arugula and added spinich so it was an entree not salad. I had sabayon left and used for a mild white fish.....Delicious!

