Rating: 3
Tried this last night and it worked a lot better than I expected. I have just learned to work with the type of make-shift double boiler used in this recipe, but the sauce turned out beautifully. Regarding some of the previous negative reviews...I took the introduction to the dish at face value when it said the disc had a "delicate" flavor and didn't expect much flavor. I was disappointed at first taste of the finished sauce, but kept tweaking the salt and pepper. That was the way to go as the addition of a little more of both REAL highlighted the flavor combo of the sauce. This one's a keeper.

